<br>
The start time for this raid is 7p PST.  All attending the raid need to meet in TM in the cave near the zone line to Grimling Forest.  <br>
<br>
For those that will be arriving early, you can pull bats and sonic wolves near the zone entrance but please do not move to the fort until we move as one force.<br>
<br>
The raid strategy is as follows (and is dependent on who attends and may be changed without prior notice):<br>
<br>
Makiko - puller<br>
Powpow - MA<br>
Hikmer - SA<br>
<br>
We will set up in a spot near the fort with the casters in the back, melee in front.  Makiko will pull from the fort and will pull the mob to the melee.  In no instance should anyone rush forward to &quot;assist&quot; Makiko.  Mak will work on bringing us one mob at a time using FD.  Makiko's role will be puller only.  We will start out as one large group (set up in smaller groups as always) and may eventually be able to separate the pulls so each group can get xp.  <br>
<br>
